              <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-ink-700">₹22,500 one-time</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-ink-700">4</td>
              <td class="py-3 pr-4 font-medium text-ink-900"><a class="text-brand-700 hover:underline" href="/vyapar-alternative/">Vyapar</a></td>
              <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-ink-700">Mobile-first GST billing, lighter accounting</td>
              <td class="py-3 pr-4 text-ink-700">Free mobile; ~₹3,399/yr paid</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs italic text-ink-500">Prices as of June 2026; verify current. All prices exclude 18% GST. Nidhi Books: from ₹399/month (first app, unlimited users; +₹99/mo per add-on).</p>
    </div>
  </section>

